              <h2 class="text-primary mb-5">about</h2>
                  <p class="lead text-muted">Hello, my name is Edwin! I live in Queens, New York. I am a full time student at <a href="http://www.laguardia.edu" target="_blank" class="lgcc text-muted">Laguardia Community College</a>. My major is New Media Technology with a concentration in Digital Media. I am proficient in HTML(5), CSS(3)  and I'm currently studying and gaining familiarity with JavaScript and its jQuery library. Aside from school I've been coding for over three years and I'm eager to begin helping others with their digital media needs whether it's Web Design, Development or video editing. When I'm not at work or at school I like to relax by building gaming PC's as well as playing video games. When I'm not gaming I like to sharpen my skills by learning different aspects of media from Adobe Premiere Pro, Adobe Photoshop, and Adobe Illustrator.</p>

				  <p class="lead text-muted">As a hobby I have taken up photography and every now and then I like to take my Canon EOS 700D out and take photos around where I live.</p>
